Function/model selection helper with trycatch

Source: R/FourPL_withWE.R
FourPL_withWE.Rd

Not exported. Strictly internal

Usage

FourPL_withWE(
  data,
  fix.a,
  fix.y0,
  starta,
  startbta,
  startc,
  startk,
  starty0,
  maxiter,
  algorithm = "lm",
  warnOnly = FALSE,
  inflection.point = c("explicit", "implicit"),
  time.scale = c("linear", "log")
)

Arguments

fix.a

Fix a as the actual maximum germination percentage at the end of the experiment.

fix.y0

Force the intercept of the y axis through 0.

inflection.point

Either "explicit" or "implicit". See Details.

time.scale

Either "linear" for fitting a four-parameter logistic function or "logarithmic" for fitting a four-parameter log-logistic function.
